scripts.test-report: rm -rf cypress/results mochawesome-report && cypress run --browser chrome || true && npx mochawesome-merge 'cypress/results/mochawesome_0*.json' > ./cypress/results/mochawesome_all.json && npx marge -f mochawesome ./cypress/results/mochawesome_all.json
scripts.test-report-windows: rmdir /s /q cypress\results mochawesome-report && cypress run --browser chrome || exit 0 && npx mochawesome-merge "cypress\results\mochawesome_0*.json" > .\cypress\results\mochawesome_all.json && npx marge -f mochawesome .\cypress\results\mochawesome_all.json
